  "text": "A key issue in the cited literature is the cyclical properties of these flows. Table 3 reports correlations and relative standard deviations of hiring rates, job finding rates, [CITATION_1] and separation rates with real GDP. Figure 1 plots selected series. The table and the figure indicate the following patterns, all with respect to real GDP. [CITATION_2] The correlations for Fallick and Fleischman and JOLTS series should be interpreted with care as the original series are very short time series. [CITATION_3] ) yields a flow that is moderately counter-cyclical.",
